extends baseEmail

block content
  div.email-header
    div.thanks-message WELCOME TO WINSUBZ
    div.verify-message We're glad to have you here

  main.email-body
    h2.greeting Hi #{firstName},

    p
      | I’m 
      strong Godwin Inyene
      | , the founder of Winsubz. I just wanted to personally reach out and say 
      strong welcome onboard.

    p
      | I saw that you signed up recently, and honestly, it means a lot to me. 
      | Not just because you joined, but because you're trusting us to help make your 
      | digital payments simpler, faster, and more reliable.

    p
      | Winsubz was built to solve a real problem — the frustration of buying data, 
      | paying bills, or recharging airtime without delays or inflated prices.
      | Our goal is to give you a seamless experience whether you're topping up 
      | for yourself, running a VTU business, or helping friends and family stay connected.

    h3(style="margin-top:25px") Getting Started

    p Here are a few simple steps to start using Winsubz:

    ul
      li Log in to your dashboard
      li Generate your personal wallet funding account
      li Transfer funds to the account to automatically credit your wallet
      li Start buying cheap data, airtime, electricity tokens, and cable subscriptions instantly

    p
      | Once your wallet is funded, you can perform transactions instantly with some of the best VTU rates available.

    table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
      tbody
        tr
          td(align='left')
            table(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
              tbody
                tr
                  td
                    a(href=`${url}`, target='_blank') Go to your dashboard

    p(style="margin-top:20px")
      | If you ever feel stuck, confused, or just want to say hi, I’d really love to hear from you. 
      | Even if it’s something small, feel free to reach out — I read many of the messages myself.

    p
      | I also want you to know there’s a real person on the other side rooting for you.

    p
      | Warm regards,
      br
      strong Godwin Inyene
      br
      | Founder, Winsubz